data.title: Gus Johnson Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Gus Johnson with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Was a football, basketball and baseball star in high school

Was a four-time letter winner in baseball in college

Worked briefly at local TV stations in Waco, Texas; Huntsville, Alabama; and Washington, D

C

Has worked for the Big East Network, ESPN and CBS

Has done announcing for the NBA, NCAA, college hockey, Canadian Football League; NFL; mixed martial arts; Olympics and boxing

Practices martial arts, including kung fu and jujitsu

Is the announcer for the Madden NFL 11 video game
